### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = your-token-here

### Login correto
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

### Login incorreto (403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrong"
}

### Acesso sem token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/balance?account_id=100

### Balance conta inexistente (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/balance?account_id=999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Deposit criando conta
POST {{baseUrl}}/event
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "type": "deposit",
  "destination": "100",
  "amount": 10
}

### Deposit conta existente
POST {{baseUrl}}/event
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "type": "deposit",
  "destination": "100",
  "amount": 10
}

### Balance conta existente
GET {{baseUrl}}/balance?account_id=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

